_2",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":3,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":3,"parameters":["\"Oh, really?\""]},{"code":0,"indent":3,"parameters":[]},{"code":411,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":111,"indent":3,"parameters":[1,20,0,20,1]},{"code":108,"indent":4,"parameters":["数値が50以上＝アーマーブレイクの第三段階の状態"]},{"code":408,"indent":4,"parameters":["かなりボロボロの状態"]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"...If we're going that far, maybe tight-fitting swim trunks would be"]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["better after all.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"I still feel like this way is more reasonable.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["アーマーブレイク表情一覧_3",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["Rio"]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"(Huh...? Am I being pitied, by any chance!?)\""]},{"code":0,"indent":4,"parameters":[]},{"code":411,"indent":3,"parameters":[]},{"code":108,"indent":4,"parameters":["数値が0以上＝アーマーブレイクの第四段階の状態"]},{"code":408,"indent":4,"parameters":["全裸"]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"What on earth... I hate wearing swim trunks so much that I can see"]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["the president's naked body.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"-...Really, there's no way that's possible.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":4,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":4,"parameters":["\"Yeah. Looks like you're tired.\""]},{"code":0,"indent":4,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":3,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":3,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":412,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":205,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,{"list":[{"code":16,"indent":null},{"code":0}],"repea